data.description: Here's your chance to own a bit of Harrodsburg's history! Known locally as 'The Freeman House', this 1915 historic gem is ready for new owners to love! This home is quaint and spacious with 4 large bedrooms and 2 and a half baths. From the library, to the intricate dining room, this home brings period charm into the modern age! Some of the features include gorgeous pocket doors, detailed moulding, stunning fireplaces, tall ceilings, hardwood floors and so much more! Mini split systems were added throughout the home so heating and cooling the home is a breeze! A three car detached garage is perfect for all of your vehicles and hobbies! Situated on over 2 acres, with gorgeous views of the surrounding countryside- it is sure to delight! Schedule your tour today!
